{"tid":1486251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有人唔明 勇武同和理非 係紅臉白臉 ，good cop bad cop.互相配合先有用，冇話邊邊好d","createTime":"2019-08-18T22:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T05:44:15.000Z","uid":24615,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"589b80c2486a529981f25e5556c436eac9cad0c2","tid":1486251,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:12:54.000Z","msg":"勇武一輪 燒下狗屋燒下狗車<br />\n再和理非番170萬人一家大細<br />\n<br />\n係比政府一個下台階（如果佢有心回應）<br />\n亦係一個警告 就係勇武完 都有咁多人支持<br />\n下一輪勇武 可能就會升級<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個警告就係 勇武人數唔多 破壞性有限<br />\n但和理非有200萬人 如果呢200萬人行動升級少少<br />\n（少少 少少就夠，例如真係每人㩒1000美金）<br />\n<br />\n同時呢200萬 係勇武既預備役 你再迫香港人 <br />\n就有更多人加入玩火玩磚頭既行列<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一味和理非 佢唔撚洗理你<br />\n一味勇武 市民驚左你 佢又係咁鎮壓你"},{"pid":"ba6432a9c5056942e5879ac7b1931e035f4e09f2","tid":1486251,"uid":251119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:14:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">從今日開始，不再分和理非定勇武，總之做到野既就係香港人！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[細思極恐] 懷疑中共策劃緊另一場陰謀，已經成功瓦解緊成場運動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486236</a>"},{"pid":"659b03c10f24c62257eaa20e9f8880b6e0123eec","tid":1486251,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:24:20.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"674b65a2fc29e6c97a7c9ff9ce6146f71d26019e","tid":1486251,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:34:50.000Z","msg":"都係香港人<br />\n核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"636fc4483942990bcd6448832e49a94628f0538d","tid":1486251,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:40:43.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"fb37bf69db36cd896e0bc0cd67291f844b7b3793","tid":1486251,"uid":24615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T22:40:55.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"101a4b1fa9ec1af7f0a8c9fe6b9f038c1241ff07","tid":1486251,"uid":278723,"like":2,"dislike